msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Dersom du er utanfor USA, anbefaler vi NOWPayments (lavaste avgifter, "
"direkte til lommeboka di). Dersom du er i USA, er Stripe Crypto òg ein val. "
"Du kan aktivere fleire tenester og la besøkarane dine velja!"

